name: `Html` module and `stagger` wrapper
body:
- add `Html` module for DOM animations
- add `stagger` wrapper
- `stagger` now implements `tweenable` interface and supports `then`, `tune` and `generate` methods
- add `resume` public method for `tween` and `tweenables`
- animations now `pause` and `resume` on page `visibilityChange`
- fix `then` chains issue
- performance improvements

name: Return the `mojs` global.
body: The release returns `mojs` global to fix the helpers reference issue. Still works with `es2015` imports and `require` statements.

name: define mojs as umd module with es2015, reuqire and commonjs support
body: This release fixes broken module definitions.

name: New tweening engine
body:
Completely rewritten tweening engine - now faster, much more robust with exhaustive `API`.
Rewritten `Shape`, `ShapeSwirl` and `Burst` modules.

Breaking changes (please see [API](https://github.com/legomushroom/mojs/blob/master/api/index.md) section for more info):
- Tweens and Other Modules now have `play` instead of `start`/`run`
- `yoyo` property renamed to `isYoyo`
- All callbacks now work in certain point of time - like timeline. So can fire on both forward and backward directions
- `Burst`: `childOptions` property now named `children`

name: Swap Timeline and Tween, new Stagger module, add Path easing
body:
- swap Timeline and Tween responsibility
- add Path easing
- refactored Stagger module to receive any module
- refactor
- some docs coverage

name: Add svg path easing, fix easing options, add motion-path onPosit callback
body:
- add svg path easing
- add bezier and svg path easing options to all modules
- add onPosit callback to motion-path

name: Add motion arc, motion blur and bezier easing
body:
- add **bezier easing**
- add **motion arc**
- add **motion blur** on motion path
- add **"ease"** easing functions
- start work on **docs auto gen with grock**
- **backward compatibility break** - renamed easing functions to shortcuts:
  - quadratic  -> quad
  - quartic -> quart
  - quintic -> quint
  - sinusoidal  -> sin
  - exponential -> expo
  - circular -> circ

body:
Fix broken link for the main file in `package.json`.
